{
  "stem": "25639.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And of course, this was a way that they weeded us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And those people just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Our lives were cheap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] As a slave laborer, we lived on the factory grounds, surrounded by electric wire fences.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Across from the electric wire fences, away from the-- the factory and our barrack, we could see just charming little summer homes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Flowers, very neatly trimmed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we saw, sometimes, children, and civilians, and we thought that they were-- they belonged to the SS, that that's where they lived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Only to find out later that they were the civilians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "These were charming little summer homes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They moved out of the city and moved into their summer homes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The Continental Gummi-- Gummi Werke is, if not largest, it-- it could be the second largest factory in all of Europe today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was founded by Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And through research, I found out it was found by Jews way back in the middle of the 19th century, in the-- around 1850.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And maybe it was even earlier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I could give it to you exactly later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And on its board of directors, there were a number of Jews, and non-Jews as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And as we go year by year from the time that Hitler came to power, you could see that the board of directors-- the Jews were removed from the board of directors.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Until 1939, there was only one token Jew on the board of directors of the Continental Gummi Werke, and this person apparently was a diplomat from Sweden.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "After 1939, he, too, was no longer there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the factory was totally taken over by-- by the SS and by the government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, indeed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were civilians who worked there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, they were in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
